{"tid":91672,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"赤西仁搭地鐵隨手抓吊環就超帥　網民驚：還以為拍雜誌","createTime":"2017-01-23T04:26:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-23T05:10:54.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"385f5ce5bcd20924ab9c0ef8931ccf384babb955","tid":91672,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T04:26:51.000Z","msg":"日本藝人赤西仁從KAT-TUN單飛6年，日前剛宣布老婆黑木梅紗懷上第2胎，整個人洋溢喜氣。他22日在Instagram分享生活照，穿著一身黑衣搭乘電車，就算打扮低調還是很引人注目，也讓粉絲驚訝大呼「好想遇到」！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/AAm74VI.img?h=410&amp;w=728&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f&amp;x=1011&amp;y=357\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FAAm74VI.img%3Fh%3D410%26w%3D728%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df%26x%3D1011%26y%3D357&h=34aa166a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲赤西仁。<br />\n<br />\n照片中，赤西仁穿著黑衣、黑褲、黑鞋，沒有特別遮掩長相，在乘客不多的電車上，獨自抓著吊環、站得筆挺，Note7起火電池惹禍三星願全權負責十分引人注目。他透露，上1次搭電車已經是很久以前，令一票粉絲激動直問「搭去哪裡呢」、「好帥，好想一起搭車」、「還以為是什麼雜誌的照片呢」、「原來仁君也搭電車，感覺好親切」。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2294/2294370.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2294%2F2294370.jpg&h=3b0dc052&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲赤西仁搭地鐵。<br />\n<br />\n赤西仁近年把重心放在歌手事業，但日前宣布演出大陸電視劇《大潑猴》，還特地飛到上海參加發布會。他將在戲中飾演「二郎神」楊戩，跟吳克群、林峰、蔣夢婕等人合作，先前還親自在微博傳達消息，「我對這個故事很感興趣，而且還是在大陸工作」，期待能讓大陸粉絲看到他努力的成果。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/AAm5psj.img?h=410&amp;w=728&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f&amp;x=712&amp;y=254\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FAAm5psj.img%3Fh%3D410%26w%3D728%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df%26x%3D712%26y%3D254&h=7cba943a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲赤西仁跟林峰、吳克群合作，演出大陸電視劇《大潑猴》。"},{"pid":"bef602ac69af134bb7da4c283cf1de4b26ffb42f","tid":91672,"uid":10975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T04:29:26.000Z","msg":"林峰同吳克群out晒fo"},{"pid":"8f45e72a0821e63cb1e946cceabc70883ba26b27","tid":91672,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T04:51:53.000Z","msg":"屌你老母啲圖真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13215cecd3905fdd77802b65c0cfd17c1609b3fb","tid":91672,"uid":18587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T05:00:59.000Z","msg":"以為吊到體操選手咁"},{"pid":"c38729a3bc4770e974dd73407943aede5fa7085b","tid":91672,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T05:02:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ce345fd46dacc37bca188c7ce5e34eb5543b89b","tid":91672,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T05:03:59.000Z","msg":"垃圾新聞黎講，呢單上唔上到top10<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"919e557de8b435b731c5f60ee94e59198802d75f","tid":91672,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T05:05:52.000Z","msg":"馬總統看錶"},{"pid":"db4748e8e4f8677490371614538b75c6385a0ce9","tid":91672,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T05:10:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為吊到體操選手咁</blockquote><br />\n我都以為係喺地鐵做體操"}]}